RELEASE
Section::::Release.
The film premiered at the Glasgow Film Festival on 26 February 2017. The film was released on 6 April 2017 by GSP Studios International.
CRITICAL RECEPTION
Section::::Critical reception.
On review aggregator website Rotten Tomatoes, the film holds an approval rating of 59% based on 17 reviews, and an average rating of 5.7/10.
